I have found results for three of the four Philadelphia teams in the MLB, NBA, NFL, and NHL, but not for the fourth NHL team. Here's a list of the first championship wins for each of the three teams I found:

1. Philadelphia Phillies (MLB): The Phillies won their first World Series championship in 1980, defeating the Kansas City Royals.

2. Philadelphia 76ers (NBA): The 76ers won their first NBA championship in 1967, beating the San Francisco Warriors 4-2 in the 1967 NBA Finals.

3. Philadelphia Eagles (NFL): The Eagles won their first Super Bowl championship in 2018, beating the New England Patriots in Super Bowl LII.

I couldn't find any results for the Philadelphia team in the NHL. If you can provide more information, such as the name of the team, I may be able to assist you further.
